| James + LyAnh Wedding | The Lido house, Newport Beach.

Last weeekend we had fortunate to capture one of the Elegant, luxury wedding in Southern California for James and LyAnh, The Wedding got special rooftop afterparty sponsor by very famous Dom Perignon  Champagne, one bottle could cost $1500. 

Let talk about the venue, The Lido House in Newport Beach is actually a boutique hotel ran by Marriot and of of the Marriot’s Autograph Collection. If you ever visit Lido House in Newport Beach, you will see why it is one of my favorite venues in the entire Southern California area. The beachy vibe together with the nautical decor catch my attention immediately and I couldn’t be more in love. What a dream venue to photograph a wedding at! I consider myself lucky just doing my job. If you are looking for an amazing venue with the coastal feel, make sure you check The Lido House out, you won’t regret it.
